title: 10/12: Mailbag (Recorded Fri.)! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
After a look at some news updates, Adam and Ben are answering your questions via Apple Podcasts (3:50) to start the show. Then we get to the fantasyfootball@cbsi.com inbox with some Fantasy Regulators (15:00), trade questions (20:30) and Start or Sit (28:15) followed by some quick lineup questions from Twitter (40:40).
